flowchart LR
    subgraph Client[用户侧]
        Browser[浏览器]
    end

    subgraph Nodes[被监控设备]
        Agent[Windows / Linux Agent]
        Queue[(SQLite WAL 待传队列)]
        Agent -->|先落盘| Queue
    end

    subgraph Server[2 核 2 GiB 单机服务器]
        Nginx[Nginx\nHTTPS 与反向代理]
        App[FastAPI + Vue 静态资源\n单副本 / 单 Worker]
        Scheduler[APScheduler\n离线检查与数据清理]
        Database[(PostgreSQL 17\n历史 / latest / 告警)]
        Backup[pg_dump 压缩备份\n恢复演练]

        Nginx --> App
        App --> Database
        Scheduler --> Database
        Database --> Backup
    end

    subgraph Delivery[交付链路]
        Repo[GitHub Repository]
        CI[GitHub Actions\n测试与构建]
        Registry[GHCR\n固定版本镜像]
        Compose[Docker Compose]
        Repo --> CI --> Registry --> Compose
    end

    Browser -->|HTTPS| Nginx
    Queue -->|HTTPS 幂等批量补传| Nginx
    Compose --> App
    Compose --> Database
